Transform **gambar → video AI** dalam 30 detik! ✨ **FREE** Replicate AI powered.

## 🚀 Live Demo
[![Deploy with Vercel](https://vercel.com/button.svg)](https://vercel.com/new/clone?repository-url=https://github.com/backupghofar-commits/ai-image-to-video)

## 📱 Features
- 🎥 **Image → MP4 Video** (4-5s cinematic)
- 📱 **Mobile-first** responsive
- ⏳ **Real-time progress** tracking
- 💾 **Session history** + download
- 🌙 **Dark mode** glassmorphism UI
- 🛡️ **Full error handling**

## 🛠 Quick Setup

### Local Development
```bash
git clone https://github.com/backupghofar-commits/ai-image-to-video.git
cd ai-image-to-video
npm install
cd backend && npm install

# Copy .env
cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
# Edit REPLICATE_API_TOKEN → https://replicate.com/account/api-tokens

npm run dev
